objCBinPackProtocolList.head: Bin pack protocol list
objCBinPackProtocolList.note: Controls bin-packing Objective-C protocol conformance list items into as few lines as possible when they go over `ColumnLimit`.

objCBlockIndentWidth.head: Block indent width
objCBlockIndentWidth.note: The number of characters to use for indentation of ObjC blocks.

objCBreakBeforeNestedBlockParam.head: Break before nested block param
objCBreakBeforeNestedBlockParam.note: Break parameters list into lines when there is nested block parameters in a function call.

objCPropertyAttributeOrder.head: Property attribute order
objCPropertyAttributeOrder.note: The order in which ObjC property attributes should appear.

objCSpaceAfterProperty.head: Space after property
objCSpaceAfterProperty.note: Add a space after `@property` in Objective-C, i.e. use `@property (readonly)` instead of `@property(readonly)`.

objCSpaceBeforeProtocolList.head: Space before protocol list
objCSpaceBeforeProtocolList.note: Add a space in front of an Objective-C protocol list, i.e. use `Foo <Protocol>` instead of `Foo<Protocol>`.
